title: AOC silent on whether she will amend doomsday climate prediction as deadline looms
description: "Squad" ringleader Rep. Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez, D-N.Y., is keeping silent on whether she still stands by her ten-year deadline for action laid out in the Green New Deal.
